            </svg>
            <h1>BloodLine</h1>
            <p>Your Trusted Blood Donation Partner</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= donorName %>,</p>
            <p>We hope this message finds you well. thanks for choosing us, and we'd love to have you on board as a life-saving donor!</p>
            <h3>Your Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= donorName %></li>
                <li><strong>Age:</strong> <%= donorAge %></li>
                <li><strong>Address:</strong> <%= donorAddress %></li>
                <li><strong>Weight:</strong> <%= donorWeight %></li>
                <li><strong>Blood Type:</strong> <%= bloodType %></li>
               
            </ul>
            <p>Why donate blood?</p>
            <p>Donating blood is a simple act that can save multiple lives. Every unit you donate can be the difference between life and death for those in critical need.</p>
            <p>If you'd like to get started or need more information, please visit our website or contact us directly.</p>
            <p>Thank you for considering to make a difference!</p>
            <p>Best Regards,<br>The BloodLine Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>devansh.dp2004@gmail.com</p>
